@Ianuda 
Back on the topic of missing tags, I have to recognize artists that have developed certain niche towards a specific content or use my "hentai sense" on the doujin covers for artist I don't recognize to get a feel for whether a certain doujin may or may not contain a tag that I'm looking for. And most of the times I'm usually right, and guess what the doujin also happen to be missing that crucial tag that might have made searching easier.

That being said though, check out Murasaki Nyaa and Dhibi(highly recommend this artist). Since you mentioned "gentle", I think these artist might have works that are right up your alley.
